overview: Grill up the carne asada, sit back and hold on as JD Films brings you the fifth release in the Dezert People Video Series. Featuring: Jesse James, Wayne Lugo, Steve Oliges, Jason McNeil, Carl Renezeder, Larry Roseler, Vildosola Racing, Camburg, Steve Sourapas, Herder Motorsports, Travis Pastrana (Subaru Rally), exclusive CORR footage and many more...
title: Dezert People 5
